Faction.name: {=allyrion}Allyrion
Faction.text: House Allyrion of Godsgrace is a major Dornish noble house.

Faction.name: {=dalt}Dalt of Lemonwood
Faction.text: House Dalt of Lemonwood is a house of landed knights from Dorne, and their head is known as the Knight of Lemonwood. Their seat of Lemonwood is located south of the mouth of the Greenblood, close to the shadow city of Sunspear.

Faction.name: {=gargalen}Gargalen
Faction.text: House Gargalen of Salt Shore is a major Dornish noble house. Their seat, Salt Shore, is located along the Summer Sea on the southern coast of Dorne.

Faction.name: {=fowler}Fowler
Faction.text: House Fowler of Skyreach is a noble house from Skyreach in Dorne. They hold the title of Warden of the Prince's Pass and watch over the Prince's Pass.

Faction.name: {=santagar}Santagar of Spottswood
Faction.text: House Santagar of Spottswood is a house of landed knights from Spottswood in Dorne. They are one of the main houses sworn to Sunspear.

Faction.name: {=chyttering}Chyttering
Faction.text: House Chyttering is a noble house of the crownlands sworn to House Baratheon of King's Landing.

Faction.name: {=farring}Farring
Faction.text: House Farring is a noble house of the crownlands.

Faction.name: {=slynt}Slynt
Faction.text: House Slynt of Harrenhal is a noble house from Harrenhal in the riverlands.

Faction.name: {=stokeworth}Stokeworth
Faction.text: House Stokeworth of Stokeworth is a noble house from the crownlands. Sworn directly to King's Landing, they live at nearby Castle Stokeworth north of the capital.

Faction.name: {=sunglass}Sunglass of Sweetport Sound
Faction.text: House Sunglass of Sweetport Sound is a noble house sworn to Dragonstone. The location of Sweetport Sound in the crownlands has not been stated.

Faction.name: {=ROTmassey}Massey
Faction.text: The Massey clan is a minor clan from the Crownlands. They are known for their skills as sailors and shipbuilders, and often serve as merchant traders and naval officers for House Targaryen. The clan holds lands near the Blackwater Bay, and its members are respected for their nautical expertise and loyalty to the Targaryens.

Faction.name: {=codd}Codd
Faction.text: House Codd is a noble house from the Iron Islands..

Faction.name: {=harlawgreygarden}Harlaw of Grey Garden
Faction.text: House Harlaw of Grey Garden is a cadet branch of the main House Harlaw that rules the eponymous island from their seat at the Ten Towers. Their seat is Grey Garden.

Faction.name: {=harlawharlawhall}Harlaw of Harlaw Hall
Faction.text: House Harlaw of Harlaw Hall is a cadet branch of the main House Harlaw that rules the eponymous island from their seat at the Ten Towers. Their seat is Harlaw Hall.

Faction.name: {=harlawharridanhill}Harlaw of Harridan Hill
Faction.text: House Harlaw of Harridan Hill is a cadet branch of the main House Harlaw that rules the eponymous island from their seat at the Ten Towers. Their seat is Harridan Hill.

Faction.name: {=harlawglimmeringtower}Harlaw of the Tower of Glimmering
Faction.text: House Harlaw of the Tower of Glimmering is a cadet branch of the main House Harlaw that rules the eponymous island from their seat at the Ten Towers. The cadet branch's seat is the Tower of Glimmering.

Faction.name: {=kenningharlaw}Kenning of Harlaw
Faction.text: House Kenning of Harlaw is a noble house from Harlaw, one of the Iron Islands.

Faction.name: {=stonetree}Stonetree
Faction.text: House Stonetree of Harlaw is a house of the Iron Islands located on the island of Harlaw. They swear allegiance to House Harlaw. They have large holdings on the island and have a decorated history.

Faction.name: {=wynch}Wynch
Faction.text: House Wynch of Iron Holt is a noble house from the island of Pyke in the Iron Islands. They are among the Greyjoys' principal bannermen.Their seat Iron Holt is on the other side of the island from the castle of Pyke, the seat of House Greyjoy.

Faction.name: {=liddle}Liddle
Faction.text: House Liddle is the formal name given to the mountain clan of the Liddles in the north that inhabit the high mountains north of the wolfswood.

Faction.name: {=wull}Wull
Faction.text: House Wull is the formal name given to the Wulls, the most powerful of the mountain clans from the north. The Wulls inhabit the area west of the Northern mountains along the Bay of Ice.The chief of the clan is known as the Wull, although at Winterfell he is given the treatment of Lord Wull

Faction.name: {=ambrose}Ambrose
Faction.text: House Ambrose is a noble house from the Reach.

Faction.name: {=chester}Chester
Faction.text: House Chester of Greenshield rules over Greenshield, one of the Shield Islands of the Reach.

Faction.name: {=costayne}Costayne
Faction.text: House Costayne of Three Towers is a noble house from Three Towers in the Reach, sworn to the Hightowers. Their castle is located on the southern coast of the Whispering Sound.

Faction.name: {=crane}Crane
Faction.text: House Crane of Red Lake is a noble house from Red Lake in the Reach. It is one of the principal houses sworn to House Tyrell.

Faction.name: {=florent}Florent
Faction.text: House Florent of Brightwater Keep is a noble house from Brightwater Keep in the Reach, one of the main houses sworn to House Tyrell of Highgarden.

Faction.name: {=fossowayciderhall}Fossoway of Ciderhall
Faction.text: House Fossoway of Cider Hall is a noble house from the Reach, one of the principal bannermen sworn to House Tyrell. Cider Hall is located at the fork of the Mander and the Cockleswent.

Faction.name: {=fossowaynewbarrell}Fossoway of New Barrel
Faction.text: House Fossoway of New Barrel is a noble house from New Barrel in the Reach, sworn to House Tyrell of Highgarden.

Faction.name: {=grimm}Grimm
Faction.text: House Grimm of Greyshield rules the island Greyshield, one of the Shield Islands of the Reach, from their castle, Grimston.

Faction.name: {=hewett}Hewett
Faction.text: House Hewett of Oakenshield rules over Oakenshield, one of the Shield Islands of the Reach.

Faction.name: {=mullendore}Mullendore
Faction.text: House Mullendore of Uplands is one of the principal noble houses from the Reach. Their seat, Uplands, is east of Oldtown. They are sworn to the Hightowers.

Faction.name: {=norcross}Norcross
Faction.text: House Norcross is a noble house from the Reach. According to semi-canon sources, they blazon their shield with a cross embattled, black on white.

Faction.name: {=peake}Peake
Faction.text: House Peake of Starpike is a noble house from Starpike in the Reach.

Faction.name: {=serry}Serry
Faction.text: House Serry of Southshield rules over Southshield, the southernmost of the Shield Islands of the Reach.

Faction.name: {=willum}Willum
Faction.text: House Willum is a noble house from the Reach.

Faction.name: {=goodbrook}Goodbrook
Faction.text: House Goodbrook is a noble house of the riverlands.

Faction.name: {=haigh}Haigh
Faction.text: House Haigh is a noble house from the riverlands. The Haighs are vassals of House Frey.

Faction.name: {=piper}Piper
Faction.text: House Piper of Pinkmaiden is one of the chief noble houses from the riverlands. Its seat at Pinkmaiden Castle is located on the Red Fork close to the border with the westerlands.

Faction.name: {=vanceatranta}Vance of Atranta
Faction.text: House Vance of Atranta is one of the two great branches of House Vance in the riverlands, the other being House Vance of Wayfarer's Rest.

Faction.name: {=caron}Caron
Faction.text: House Caron of Nightsong is one of the principal noble houses in the stormlands, sworn to Storm's End. They rule from Nightsong and hold the title Lord of the Marches, although they do not hold dominion over other marcher lords in the Dornish Marches.

Faction.name: {=grandison}Grandison
Faction.text: House Grandison of Grandview is a noble house from Grandview in the stormlands.

Faction.name: {=hasty}Hasty
Faction.text: House Hasty is a noble house of landed knights from the stormlands.

Faction.name: {=horpe}Horpe
Faction.text: House Horpe is a noble house from the stormlands.

Faction.name: {=morrigen}Morrigen
Faction.text: House Morrigen of Crow's Nest is a noble house from Crow's Nest in the stormlands..

Faction.name: {=swann}Swann
Faction.text: House Swann of Stonehelm is one of the primary noble houses of the stormlands. They are marcher lords ruling from Stonehelm over the lands surrounding the Red Watch on Cape Wrath in the eastern Dornish Marches.

Faction.name: {=wagstaff}Wagstaff
Faction.text: House Wagstaff is a noble house from the Stormlands.

Faction.name: {=Borrell}Borrell
Faction.text: House Borrell of Sweetsister is a noble house from the Vale ruling over Sweetsister, an island of the Three Sisters, and its port town, Sisterton. Their castle is Breakwater in Sisterton. House Borrell's titles include Lord of Sweetsister, Shield of Sisterton, Master of Breakwater Castle, and Keeper of the Night Lamp. They are sworn to House Sunderland, who also reside in Sisterton.

Faction.name: {=hardyng}Hardyng
Faction.text: House Hardyng is a house of landed knights in the Vale of Arryn.

Faction.name: {=lynderly}Lynderly
Faction.text: House Lynderly of the Snakewood is a noble house from the Vale of Arryn. Their castle is Snakewood and they carry the title Lord of the Snakewood.

Faction.name: {=royceofthegates}Royce of the Gates of the Moon
Faction.text: House Royce of the Gates of the Moon is a noble house from the Gates of the Moon in the Vale of Arryn. They are a cadet branch of House Royce of Runestone.

Faction.name: {=shettgulltower}Shett of Gull Tower
Faction.text: House Shett of Gull Tower is a noble house from Gull Tower in the Vale of Arryn. They are sworn to House Royce of Runestone.

Faction.name: {=sunderland}Sunderland
Faction.text: House Sunderland of the Three Sisters rules the Three Sisters, islands located in the Bite. The Sunderlands are sworn to House Arryn of the Eyrie..

Faction.name: {=templeton}Templeton
Faction.text: House Templeton of Ninestars is a noble house from Ninestars in the Vale of Arryn, a powerful knightly family sworn to House Arryn. The head of the family is given the title of Knight of Ninestars. The current head of the house is Ser Symond Templeton..

Faction.name: {=tollett}Tollett
Faction.text: House Tollett of the Grey Glen is a house from the Grey Glen in the Vale of Arryn. They are sworn to the Royces from Runestone.

Faction.name: {=waynwood}Waynwood
Faction.text: House Waynwood of Ironoaks is a noble house from Ironoaks in the Vale of Arryn. They are one of the great noble families sworn to House Arryn.

Faction.name: {=estren}Estren
Faction.text: House Estren of Wyndhall is a noble house from the westerlands. The exact location of Wyndhall has not been disclosed yet.

Faction.name: {=farman}Farman
Faction.text: House Farman of Faircastle is a noble house from Faircastle on Fair Isle, off the coast of the westerlands. They are sworn to House Lannister of Casterly Rock, and are considered among their principal bannermen. The Farmans are known for their hatred of the ironborn from the Iron Islands

Faction.name: {=marbrand}Marbrand
Faction.text: House Marbrand of Ashemark is one of the main noble houses from the westerlands. Their seat of Ashemark is located in the hilly area near where the Tumblestone begins.

Faction.name: {=moreland}Moreland
Faction.text: House Moreland is a noble house from the westerlands, with an unknown seat.

Faction.name: {=plumm}Plumm
Faction.text: House Plumm is a noble house of the westerlands.

Faction.name: {=prester}Prester
Faction.text: House Prester of Feastfires is one of the principal noble houses sworn to House Lannister of Casterly Rock. Their seat at Feastfires is located at the westernmost point of the westerlands.

Faction.name: {=ruttiger}Ruttiger
Faction.text: House Ruttiger is a house of landed knights sworn to Casterly Rock.

Faction.name: {=spicer}Spicer
Faction.text: House Spicer of Castamere is a minor noble house of the westerlands.

Faction.name: {=stackspear}Stackspear
Faction.text: House Stackspear is a noble house of the westerlands sworn to House Lannister of Casterly Rock.

Faction.name: {=vikary}Vikary
Faction.text: House Vikary is a house of landed knights sworn to Casterly Rock.

Faction.name: {=yew}Yew
Faction.text: House Yew is a house of landed knights from the westerlands.
